PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (LIARD FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of land in the Yukon Territory until March 31, 2004, and (b) repeals the Withdrawal from Disposal Order made by Order in Council P.C. 2000-873.
